Product Name: Zodiac Baracuda MX8 Swimming Pool Automatic Suction Cleaner
Product Description:
Zodiac Baracuda MX8 Swimming Pool Automatic Suction Cleaner

An efficient and powerful automatic swimming pool cleaner, the Zodiac Baracuda MX8 cleaner combines a dual cyclonic suction for a speedy, energy efficient and powerful vacuum alongside a thorough capacity for cleaning any size or shape of swimming pool.

With a wider cleaning path than competitor models and a large vacuum inlet to capture larger debris, the Zodiac Baracuda MX8 cleaner provides outstanding pool coverage, with maximum torque and easy manoeuvrability enabling for an aggressive automatic clean of swimming pool walls and floors.

The Zodiac Baracuda MX8 Automatic Swimming Pool Suction Cleaner is the best choice for solar, 2-speed and variable speed pool cleaners.

Zodiac Baracuda MX8 Automatic Swimming Pool Suction Cleaner features:

  • MaX-Drive advanced dual navigation for best pool coverage with no hang ups.
  • Thoroughly cleans floor, walls, and waterline of any size or shape pool
  • With twist locking hose enabling for a quick, secure attachment to the cleaner head
  • Cleaner includes 39 feet of hose
  • Dual Cyclonic Vacuum provides maximum suction power and extreme wall climbing ability
  • Cyclonic suction provides unsurpassed vacuum power, wider cleaning path, and largest debris intake
  • Flex-Power Turbine enables ultra-efficient operation on low flow without compromising power
  • For use on all pool surfaces
  • Minimum Pump Requirement: 3/4 Horse Power

Product Name: Zodiac Baracuda R3 Swimming Pool Automatic Suction Cleaner
Product Description:
Zodiac Baracuda R3 Automatic swimming pool suction cleaner

The Zodiac Baracuda R3 pool suction cleaner uses simple technology yet has a highly effective finish! This swimming pool cleaner is ideally used for inground pools and simply connects to either a suction point on the wall or uses your skimmer suction point.

The Zodiac R3 Automatic Suction Cleaner is suitable for most types of pool surfaces i.e. tiled, liner, concrete, vinyl, fibreglass etc. and is supplied with 10 metres of hose (10 x 1m twist lock hoses)

Zodiac Baracuda R3 Pool Suction Cleaner Features:

  • Automated cleaning which uses a Hydraulic Suction
  • The R3 is lightweight and very simple to use and set up
  • Designed with one moving part - the Duralife Diaphragm.  The strong reinforced outer ribbing makes the diaphragm significantly more durable than competitive products and past models of Baracuda Cleaner, like the G2.  The diaphragm is super easy to clean or replace and provides long lasting efficient suction
  • Extremely quiet operations
  • 10 metres of Twist & Lock Hose
  • Rotating Wheel Deflector for added assistance with easy navigation around corners, steps, ladders and drains
  • Minimum Pump Requirement: 1/2 Horse Power
  • 12 Month Warranty (Does not include the diaphragm, these can wear with bad water chemistry)

Product Name: Baracuda In-Line Leaf Trap For MX8 and B3 Cleaners
Product Description:
Baracuda In-Line Leaf Trap For MX8 and B3 Cleaners

An In-Line filter for collecting and trapping debris before it can reach the pump basket (preventing clogging), the Baracuda In-Line Leaf Trap for MX8 and B3 Automatic Suction Cleaners is suitable for use with most pools and is easy to both use and maintain.

Baracuda Suction Cleaner Leaf Trap Features

  • Has a greater capacity for leaves and debris than the average pump basket, with a convenient handle for easier cleaning and emptying
  • Connects directly to the skimmer or to the suction point
  • Includes a built-in drain plug to empty water for easier canister handling
  • Manufactured from clear UV-resistant materials so you can see when the Baracuda Leaf Trap needs emptying.
  • Unique T-trap connection meaning that all vacuum hoses remain connected while the leaf trap is removed
  • Unique design which uses the water flow of your automatic suction cleaner to create a vacuum within the trap, compacting and holding more leaves and debris (with less need for emptying as a result!)
  • Can be used when full without affecting the pump or diminishing the suction rate
  • Suitable for all pools

Product Name: Swimming Pool Automatic Roldeck Easy Cover System
Product Description:
Swimming Pool Automatic Roldeck Easy Cover System

The Roldeck Easy Cover is a highly versatile electronic powered above ground swimming pool cover system for both outdoor and indoor installation. With its two discreet slim stands the Roldeck Easy Cover is an ideal and elegant fit if space is limited around the pool.

The Roldeck Easy Cover system is suitable for pools up to 12m by 6m, and is fully automatic being calibrated  to suit the individual pool. Manufactured with high quality materials the Roldeck Easy Cover is available with a range of slats.

Easily operated from the key switch positioned on the side of the console the user can open and close the cover. As a safety feature the key can be removed when the pool is not in use.

Please call 0151 334 0222 for further details

Roldeck Easy Cover Pool System Features:-

  • Easy installed on new or existing pools
  • Easy programmed for one touch operation
  • Key switch operated - ensures no unwanted operation of the easy cover

The Roldeck Easy Cover automatic swimming pool system is also available in a Solar Powered version.

Roldeck Easy Cover Solar Powered Pool Cover Extra Features:-

  • Solar powered - eco-friendly free power with no need for extra cabling
  • Large battery capacity - will run 20 cycles without solar charge

Product Name: Skymirror Golf - One Piece In Ground Swimming Pool
Product Description:
Skymirror One Piece In Ground Swimming Pools

An affordable and high quality luxury swimming pool developed for a simpler DIY installation & complete safety, sophistication & comfort

With Skymirror One Piece In Ground Swimming Pools you get to pick the features, meaning that whatever you envision your dream pool to be can easily be made a reality and at a fraction of the price and effort of a concrete swimming pool build! Choose from a range of features including comfortable integrated loungers, spa jets, hydro massage, LED lighting and a choice of colours.

Skymirror One Piece In Ground Swimming Pools are also incredibly accommodating and safe for children to use making them an ideal swimming pool choice for families. Featuring low level safety ledges to provide peace of mind whilst the kids play in the pool, Skymirror One Piece In Ground Swimming Pools also feature variable depths (Marina model only) so that children can play comfortably in the shallow end of the pool.

Installing a Skymirror Swimming Pool

First things first - give us a call and we'll go through it with you! 0151 334 0222 - subject to everything being ok the basics are as follows; 

You will need builders to dig the hole! The Skymirror One Piece In ground Swimming Pool is ordered and is usually available for delivery anywhere between 10 days to 4 weeks.  The pool arrives on the agreed day by lorry with integrated crane and your Skymirror One Piece DIY Pool is then lifted and dropped into the hole your builders will have dug.  The pool is levelled off, pipe work put in place, back filled and finished off. 

Prior to this we can arrange for a Skymirror representative to visit the site for an inspection to make sure all is ok - one of the most important factors to consider, for instance, is access for the lorry to reach the designated place for the pool.

Planning Permission

Planning permission in most cases is not an issue, however give us a call and we'll be glad to advise 0151 334 0222.

Skymirror One Piece In Ground Swimming Pools features

  • Low level safety ledges
  • Curved large tread staircases with anti-slip surfaces
  • Wide seating areas
  • Constructed using double composite vinylester (which protects against osmosis and ensures longevity to your pool)
  • High quality honeycomb insulation layer for dramatic heat loss reduction

Skymirror One Piece In Ground DIY Swimming Pools are available as three different models: Delta, Golf & Marina.

 

Skymirror Golf (constant depth)

  • Depth: Water 1.25m & shell 1.50m
  • Beautiful romance staircase & broad seat
  • Safety ledges at 50mm & 900mm deep
  • Bench seating area
  • Anti slip on all surfaces

Skymirror Golf 2014 Prices (exclude VAT) from time to time we have offers on these pools!

  • 6m x 3.4m x 1.25m £9,275
  • 6m x 3.4m x 1.5m £9,940

  • 8m x 3.4m x 1.25m £12,953
  • 9m x 3.4m x 1.5m £14,147
  • 10m x 4m x 1.5m £14,652

Featuring a classic, elegant design the Golf is big on glamour and luxury which brings the integrated Roman steps of the Skymirror Pool design to classy prominence. With sophistication and recreation at it's heart, the Golf is an ideal pool model for family and friends to enjoy together, or for some well deserved TLC time.

  • 1 x skimmer
  • 1 x UW light, transformer & deck box
  • 1 x returns
  • 1 x low level suctions
  • 1 x vac point
  • 1 x auto top up

Skymirror One Piece In Ground Swimming Pool Warranty

Product Description:
Sargent Electrical Intelligent Leisure Battery Charger

Sargent PX310 300W Leisure Battery Charger – Smart 3-Stage Charging for Motorhomes & Caravans

The PX310 is a 300W, 3-stage intelligent leisure battery charger and power supply designed for leisure vehicle applications. It provides power for both battery charging and 12-volt appliances. The integrated LCD display shows battery charging status and allows setup for different battery chemistries. A PSU mode allows the charger to be used without a battery fitted, and the Silent mode avoids noise during overnight charging. 

Compatibility and Use

This leisure battery charger is configured to work with standard lead-acid, Gel, AGM (Absorbed Glass Mat), and Lithium batteries. The recommended battery capacity is 70 to 220Ah. The Sargent PX310 can be safely left switched on as required.

  • Input Voltage: 200 - 240V AC
  • Charging Current (max): 20A @ 14.5V
  • Boost Voltage: 14.7V (max)
  • Float Voltage: 13.8V (max)
  • Compatible Batteries: Flooded, Gel, AGM, Lithium
  • Battery Size: 70 - 220Ah
  • Cooling Method: Intelligent fan with Silent Mode
  • Dimensions (LxWxH): 221 x 157 x 69mm
  • Weight: 1.55kg

Product Name: Dometic Waeco CRX50 Fridge 12volt 24v Compressor Marine Campervan Refrigerator
Product Description:
Dometic Waeco CRX50 12volt 24v Compressor Fridge Marine Campervan Refrigerator

A versatile compressor fridge with a uniquely removable freezer compartment, the Waeco CRX50 is perfect for use in marine, campervans, caravans and motorhomes

With the added benefits of having a low consumption of energy (so low that it can feasibly be run off solar panels!), the Waeco CRX50 2 Way Compressor Fridge has an ample 48L refrigerator capacity which can also maintain between 5 - 7 degrees even under the pressure of tropical temperatures!

What makes the Dometic Waeco CRX50 different from a standard CR50 model?

The Waeco CRX50 2 Way Caravan, Marine & Motorhome Fridge still has all the outstanding features of the original, standard model but with the added bonus of a completely versatile configuration in the form of a removable freezer compartment, meaning that you can adapt and use your Waeco CRX50 to suit your needs whenever and wherever you need it. As a result, the Waeco CRX50 Compressor Fridge can be used as a conventional fridge/freezer, full fridge or full freezer. The Waeco CRX50 also now features a slightly chamfered rear wall, this helps clear the strengthening pieces found in many vans at floor level, and also helps for a 'snug' fit in marine applications where the hull turns inwards near the bilges.

Dometic Waeco Compressor fridge CRX50 the features:

  • New soft touch control panel
  • Intelligent electronic control of the compressor speed - up to 25% less energy consumption
  • 5 different temperature settings
  • 2 stage battery protection
  • Chamfered cabinet at rear base to help clear the campervan or caravan side
  • Bright led interior light with infrared sensor
  • Large bottle holder
  • Door tray
  • Salad bin
  • 2 years warranty

Versatile and engineered for ease of use and continual high performance for your campervan or boat

The door of the Waeco CRX50 2-Way Compressor Fridge can be hinged on either side to conveniently accommodate for a left or right opening, whilst the décor panel can also be replaced to suit the interior of your campervan. The Waeco CRX50 Compressor 2-Way Fridge also features a venting position in the door lock to maintain freshness and airflow when the fridge isn't in use and a double locking mechanism so the door can be secured at the top and bottom.

Inflatable Awning for Campervan and Motorhome 

The Vango Kela V awning is the perfect addition to your campervan or motorhome. The AirBeam system provides a strong and rigid structure that is quick and easy to pitch. The Vango Kela 5 is inflated and deflated in just a few minutes leaving you more time to enjoy the outdoors. Attach to the side of your vehicle using one of the 4 attachment options. The Kela V provides addition living space for family and friends as well as extra storage space for all those holiday essentials.

Vango Kela V Low, Standard and Tall Awnings Include

The Vango Kela V touring awning fits a wide range of campervan and motorhomes and is available in sizes Kela V Low, Standard and Tall. Select the correct size for your vehicle from the drop down options.

Vango Kela V Standard Low and Tall Awnings Features:

  • Sky Track II System - Flexible hanging system to attach lighting, sky liners and storage solutions
  • Two mesh doors - help keep bugs out
  • Skylight Windows - enhance light during the day and enjoy star gazing at night
  • High Visibility Guy lines with tidies
  • Sentinel Pro Fabric - double ripstop construction, UV resistant and highly waterproof
  • Low Level Ventilation - reduces condensation
  • Diamond clear windows - for maximum light and clear visibility
  • Fully sewn in groundsheet - flat entry for easy access to wheelchairs and pushchairs
  • Zipped Curtains - for added privacy in your awning
  • Power cable entry point and tidies
  • King pole doors - prop open the front door to create a canopy, requires optional king poles.

Vango Kela 5 Tall Standard and Low Awnings Include:

  • Oversized bag with tensioning straps to easily pack away your awning
  • Multiple attachments: 6mm kador strip, roof straps and roof bar tabs 
  • Double Action Pump
  • Steel ground pegs
  • Mallet
  • Storm straps

Optional Extras:

  • Footprint groundsheet protector GP005
  • Carpet CP105
  • Inner tent bedroom BR001
  • Sky liners
  • Drive away fixing kit

The standard fixing kit is 6mm x 6mm. However, if you have a Fiamma awning you will require a 4mm x 6mm kit. Click here to select the drive away kit you require.
Product Warranty: The Vango Kela V drive away awning comes with a two year warranty from the date of purchase. Register your new awning with Vango online to extend it to three years.
Product Availability: Vango Kela V Awnings are sent via next working day delivery

Product Description:
Dometic PW1000 Motorhome and Caravan Wall Awning

  • Compact awning housing

  • High quality awning cloth made in one piece – no welding seams

  • Choice of mounting adapters, in 17 different variations.

Dometic Perfectroof PR2500 Roof Mounted Motorhome and Caravan Awning
Product Description:
Dometic Perfectroof PR 2500 Motorhome and Caravan Awning

The Dometic Perfectroof PR 2500 is the roofmounted awning option for larger, 4.50 m and beyond, caravans, campervans and motorhomes, and also long wheelbase panel vans and van conversions. There is no lighter and more compact roof awning on the market to rival the Perfectroof PR 2500. The roof mounted housing does not interfere with the motorhomes aerodynamics. End caps are constructed from 100% aluminium to make the awning extra resistant to shock and sudden impacts. The patented locks on both sides of the front rail ensure perfect closure of the awning, as well as additional safety when driving your motorhome, or towing your caravan. The Dometic Perfectroof PR2500's Smooth and rapidly operating running gear is operated with a patented "Easy lock" telescopic crank handle, which is easily adaptable to the correct height for your motorhome or caravan. Also available with a fully integrated motor, [ *factory fitted ] operating on 230v AC or, 12v DC, and incorporating a manual override for emergency operation.



Features:

  • Designed for mounting on the roof of the camper, motorhome or caravan
  • Compact lightweight awning housing
  • Patented locks either end of the front rail, for worry free closing when traveling
  • Aluminium end caps, resistant to shock and impact
  • Lengths from 3.0 to 6.0 m, extension up to 2.75 m
  • High quality awning cloth made in one piece – no welding seam
  • Support legs with Easy Lock Flipper © - no accidental dropping possible
  • Telescopic crank handle for different vehicle heights
  • Electric winding  [ Optional, factory fit* ] Mains 230 volts or 12 volts
  • Choice of adaptors in 9 different variations

Choice of Colours

  • Case colour in:-     White, Silver or Anthracite
  • Canopy colour in:- Grey or Blue

Niveko One Piece Swimming Pool
Product Description:
Niveko One Piece Swimming Pools

Niveko Swimming Pools, the answer to your dreams without the expense of a traditionally built pool!

Niveko Skimmer - Standard

The Classic domestic style pool comes with one or two skimmers and a choice of colours and sizes. Options include rounded corners and a range of step options.

Niveko Overflow - Multi

This is the Overflow option, with the choice of internal or external steps. The overflow can be finished with a PVC grill or with a natural looking stone grill in a choice of colours.

Niveko Overflow – Endless

Giving the swimmer the impression that the pool goes on forever this infinity edge pool with a natural stone finish option is just stunning.

Niveko Overflow – Advance

Instead of a grill type system this Niveko pool has a continuous slot around the pool for the water to flow into. For a magical finish this Niveko pool is finished with natural stone or stainless steel.

 

Not sure what to go for? here's a Niveko pool we suggest, it's cost, and what you need to know.

What size?

If you want to keep it simple and you have the space then we’d recommend you go for either the 7m x 3.7m or the 8m x 3.7m Niveko pool with corner steps. These sizes are either side of what has been an ever popular pool size of 24ft x 12ft, most people usually go for one of these options.

What extra costs are there?

The cost of the pool does not include delivery from Czech Republic, this is £4750, also not included is the cost of a mobile crane, a guidance quotation for the rental of a crane from Ainscough crane hire (a national crane company) as of January 2018 was £1250, this is for a days use (8 hours), Pool filter and pump £540 approx.

Using a 7m x 3.5m pool as an example the cost would be:

  • 7m x 3.5 metre pool
  • Delivery
  • Crane
  • Pump and filter
  • Starting from £24,000

Do I get help?

Included in the price of the pool is a Niveko technician who will supervise the lifting of the pool from the truck and into position.  The technician is available for a second day to supervise the concrete backfilling of the pool; this does not necessarily have to be the next day and could be a week or maybe 2 down the line.

What do I have to do?

Decide where you want your Niveko pool to go, check whether access can be achieved with a delivery lorry, and check with us, sometimes we can arrange a no obligation site visit to make sure all is ok.  Next arrange for the hole to be dug and the base concreted, your local builders can do this, but remember the dimensions of the pool are the internal measurements not external.  The cost of the builders is in addition to everything else listed above.

Not the pool for you?

If this is not for you then we suggest you have at the Niveko catalogue, and maybe give us a call on 0151 334 6252 or get us on live chat, we'll be glad to advise.

Jump in!

 Delivery and installation

 Niveko bring a pool to the UK's Spatex show

Delivery of the Niveko One-Piece Swimming Pool depends on your location and is approximately £4750

Dometic Motorhome & Caravan Perfect Roof Camp Room
Product Description:
Dometic Motorhome & Caravan Perfect Roof Camp Room

For all Dometic Awnings with support legs

Previously manufactured by Prostor, the Dometic Perfect Roof camp room awning easily and quickly creates an additional living or storage space. Designed to be simple, it takes just one person to erect it. The material for the windows is PVC, have zip closures, and come as standard with mosquito screens and curtains, which even allows the camp room to be used as sleeping space when required. If you cover the underside of the vehicle with a standard supplied skirt you will get a completely waterproof and wind-breaking construction.

The Perfect Wall Camp Room come with:

  • 10x Pegs for Camproom Side and Front Panel Skirting
  • 10x Tension Pegs
  • 4x Leg Pegs
  • 1 x Carry bag

Which Camp room do I need?

Step 1: Identify if you have a wall (perfect wall) mounted or roof (perfect roof) mounted awning. Click here for the camp room suitable for the Perfect Wall.

Step 2: Find the correct length - So, if you have a 3.5m awning you need a 3.5m camp room.

Step 3: Find the correct height - The sides come in different heights, you need to measure from the floor to the bottom of the awning case and choose form the sizes below

Dometic RML 9430/9435 Caravan Motorhome Fridge Freezer 3 way
Product Description:
Dometic RML 9430/9435 12v Gas and Mains Motorhome & Caravan Fridge Freezer

Motorhomes and Caravans are getting ever more compact, and every millimetre counts when it comes to designing the onboard interior, and the need for ample refrigerator space with compact dimensions continues to be a goal for the market leaders in Motorhome and Caravan fridge freezers. Dometic has introduced a new line of solutions, with a width of just 468 millimetres.

The first two models to arrive in the Motorhome and Caravan after market, are:

The Dometic RML 9430 with battery ignition system* and the  9435 with automatic energy selection (AES) ** – both with a capacity of 147 litres.

* What is the battery ignition system?

A: The Battery Ignition System on the RM 9430, means that it has a small unit containing a lithium battery, and you must select the power source (12v, Gas, Mains) Manually on the control panel.

**What is the Automatic Energy Selection (AES) ?

A: The Automatic Energy Selection (AES) means that the motorhome fridge freezer will automatically select the power source in use, for example, switching from 240v to 12v whilst travelling, and then back to mains power when the Motorhome or Caravan has hook-up.

The two pioneers of Dometic’s latest motorhome & caravan fridge freezer generation have integrated door handles (see pictures), and, despite their extremely compact outside dimensions the 9-Series motorhome & caravan fridge freezer has ample capacity inside. The fridge cabinet is organised by short and long trays, drawers with partitions and bottle holders as well as four height-adjustable door racks, a removable 12-litre freezer compartment and bright LED strip lights add the usual finishing touches we have all come to expect from Dometic. 

Dometic RML Motorhome & Caravan Fridge Freezer Features:

  • Freezer compartment down to -12°C
  • Absolutely silent
  • 1 short shelf and 2 long shelves
  • 4 adjustable shelves
  • Removable 12-litre freezer compartment
  • Door handles in automotive design
  • LED strip light
  • With battery-powered ignition unit
  • Requires Ventilation via 2 x LS300 Vents(Available seperately
  • All gas appliances must be fitted by a qualified gas engineer, failure to comply may affect your warranty.

Dometic NRX60 Compressor Motorhome & Campervan Fridge Freezer
Product Description:
Dometic NRX60 Compressor 3 In 1 Motorhome & Caravan Fridge Freezer

This 55 Litre Compressor 3 In 1 Fridge Freezer is perfect for caravans, motorhomes and campervans

A versatile compressor fridge with a removable freezer compartment with added benefits of low energy consumption, this means that it can easily run using solar panels. Unlike the previous model, the NRX60 has a 55 Litre capacity and has a layer of polyurethane insulation to maintain the cool temperatures inside.

What makes the NRX60 Motorhome Fridge Freezer different from the CRX65?

The Dometic NRX60 Caravan and Motorhome Fridge Freezer has a bevelled edge on the backside so it can fully utilise the most space in a small area, such as caravan or motorhome. This 55 litre capacity NRX60 fridge, and a 6.1 litre freezer has a completely removable freezer compartment, much like the previous model, this means that you can fully utilise the fridge area if you have no need for the freezer. As a result of this, you can use the Dometic NRX60 compressor fridge as a conventional fridge/freezer, a full fridge or even a full freezer in your motorhome or caravan.

Dometic NRX60 Motorhome & Caravan Compressor Fridge Freezer Features:

  • 3 in 1 solution with removable freezer compartment: cooling, freezing or both at the same time.
  • Intelligent electronic control of the compressor speed - up to 25% less energy consumption
  • Fan speed automatically adjusts to the ambient temperature
  • Perfect temperature control due to new design soft touch panel
  • Bright LED light with infrared sensor
  • Door lock with dual function
  • Stainless steel door
  • Standard or flush mount installation frame
  • 230V connection with low priced mains adaptor

Dometic Waeco CoolMatic CD 20 Compressor Campervan Fridge

The CoolMatic CD 20 Campervan Fridge is a space saver when it comes to campervan or motor home fridges. They have been built to utilize unused space in such small quarters, such as a pull out drawer.

Product Description:
Labcraft Astro Caravan Motorhome LED Awning Light

 

The Labcraft Astro Awning Light is a perfect awning light for your caravan, campervan, or motorhome and uses 5 times less power than a 10W halogen bulb.

  • Size : L 520mm x W 44mm x H 31mm

Ideal for installing above the exterior door of your Caravan, Motorhome or Camper.

Quick to install, compact design

The LED strip sits within a slim aluminium housing which conceals the fixings; and with ABS snap-on end caps, this compact light unit is quick and easy to install to your campervan,caravan or motorhome.

Waterproof to IP66

The PCB driver, components and LEDs are completely encased within a polycarbonate extrusion, which protects against water ingress.

Product Name: Truma Therme TT2 Caravan Campervan Complete 230v Water Heater
Product Description:
Therme TT2 Complete Electric Water Heater


The Truma Therme TT2 electric water heater has been specifically designed for caravans, campervans and motorhomes and is both lightweight and compact. Featuring a 5 litre hot water storage tank, the Therme is able to store and supply hot water of up to 65°C for tasks such as washing hands or dishes.

Less wasted heat, versatile operation

By using existing warmth from the air heating system pipes in your respective caravan, campervan or motorhome, the Therme TT2 Heater can heat water without using extra energy. Additionally the Therme has an internal 230V mains electric heater element with 300W heating output, which enables water to be heated using site electricity when the air heater system is not running or you need rapid access to hot water.

What's included and can it be used with a water pump?

The Truma Therme includes a control panel and a drain and aeration valve. Additionally the Therme can be used with all regular submerged water pumps up to a maximum of 1.2 bar.

Please note - The TT2 is not suitable for use with pressurised systems – it may only be used with microswitched systems as per the installation manual.

Option Set: PV Logic Flexi Solar Panel Kit
Product Description:
PV Logic Semi-Flexible Solar Panel Kit with Charge Controller

Mono High Density Semi Flexible Top and Rear Kit for Boat, Motorhome and Campervan

Semi-Flexible MHD Solar Panel Roof Kits are available in a range of wattage options to suit your needs, including 100w, 150w, 200w, 250w, and 290w. These solar panel kits are available for both top and rear cable exit options, meaning that the cable is either located on the top surface of the panel or the rear side. A unique design that's perfect for your canal boat! 

Ideal for boats, camper vans and motorhomes, this solar panel prevents battery drain and enables self-sufficiency making it perfect for off-grid travel. The included battery charge controller protects your battery from being overcharged and prevents reverse current drain. The 10A or 20A PWM charge controllers are capable of charging 12V and 24V single or dual batteries. Energy generation is maximised on the Canal Boat Semi Flexi Solar Battery Kit because it includes bypass diodes to minimise the effect of shadows, maximising energy generation.

Upgrade to the MPPT Pro for increased solar yield by up to 20% compared to the included 10A or 20A battery controller. The MPPT Pro artificially modifies the voltage from the solar panel to match any battery requirements, meaning that this adapts to any weather conditions to deliver maximum power with minimum electrical loss. Upgrade to the 15A MPPT Pro Charge Controller for rapid solar charging. The 15A MPPT Pro can charge dual batteries, the 20A and 30A Pro Plus models charge a single battery. The MPPT chargers come with a downloadable mobile app to monitor the performance of your solar panel so you can check on your leisure battery remotely and easily just from your phone.

 

This Canal Barge Semi Flexi Solar Panel Kit can be easily fitted to flat or curved surfaces (3cm curve per metre). Easily bond this semi-flexible solar panel to painted aluminium, metal, GRP and fibreglass using the included Henkel MS939 elastic adhesive. For land based vehicles, use the glue pattern below to ensure airflow under the panel is achieved to prevent head build-up and potential warping under extreme heat.

Semi-Flexi Solar Panel Key Features:

  • 10A or 20A Dual Battery Charger included as standard, or upgrade to the 15A, 20A or 30A Charge Controllers
  • Semi flexible panel can fit onto flat or curved surfaces (3cm per metre)
  • Perfect for curved roofs
  • In built diode protects against battery discharge
  • Tough and robust
  • Salt spray and UV light tested
  • 4-year panel warranty
  • Ideal for campervans, motorhomes & canal boats

Kit Contents:

  • 1 x 110W, 150W, 200W, 250W or 290W MHD semi-flexible solar panel with 4m cable (or 2 x 90m cable with MC4 connectors for 200W, 250W and 290W only)
  • 2 x 3m cable with MC4 connectors at one end, bare at the other (200W, 250W and 290W only)
  • 1 x shading diode
  • 1 x 10A or 20A PWM charge controller (or upgrade to the 15A, 20A or 30A MPPT charge controllers)
  • 1 x elastic adhesive (x2 for 200W, 250W and 290W models only)
  • 1 x user manual

Product Description:

Mono High Density Narrow Semi-Flexi Roof and Deck Top Kit

This 110W MHD Semi-Flexible Solar Panel Roof Kit is designed specifically to be long and narrow. A unique design that's perfect for your canal boat! Ideal for marine boats, camper vans and motorhomes, this solar panel prevents battery drain and enables self-sufficiency making it perfect for off-grid travel.

The included 10A battery charge controller protects your battery from being overcharged and prevents reverse current drain. The 10A PWM Charge Controllers are capable of charging 12V and 24V single or dual batteries. Energy generation is maximised on the Canal Boat Semi-Flexible Solar Battery Kit because it includes bypass diodes to minimise the effect of shadows, maximising energy generation.

Upgrade for efficiency!

Upgrade to the MPPT Pro for increased efficiency by up to 20% compared to the included 10A battery controller. The MPPT Pro artificially modifies the voltage from the solar panel to match any battery requirements, meaning that this adapts to any weather conditions to deliver maximum power with minimum electrical loss. Upgrade to the 15A MPPT Pro Charge Controller for rapid solar charging. The 15A MPPT Pro can charge dual batteries, the 20A and 30A Pro Plus models charge a single battery. The MPPT chargers come with a downloadable mobile app to monitor the performance of your solar panel so you can check on your leisure battery remotely and easily just from your phone.

This Semi-Flexi Solar Panel Kit can be easily fitted to flat or curved surfaces (3cm curve per metre), perfect for rounded roof campervans, motorhomes or canal boats. Easily bond this semi flexible solar panel to painted aluminium, metal, GRP and fibreglass using the included Henkel MS939 elastic adhesive. For Land Based vehicles, use the glue pattern below to ensure airflow under the panel is achieved to prevent head build-up and potential warping under extreme heat.

Semi-Flexible Solar Panel Key Features:

  • 10A dual battery charger included as standard, or upgrade to the 15A, 20A or 30A charge controllers
  • Semi flexible panel can fit onto flat or curved surfaces (3cm per metre)
  • Suitable for curved roofs
  • In built diode protects against battery discharge
  • Tough and robust
  • Works with both 12V and 24V systems
  • Salt spray and UV light tested
  • 4-year panel warranty
  • Ideal for campervans, motorhomes & canal boats

Product Description:

Please note: we cannot accept returns on bike racks. Please ensure this item is compatible with your vehicle before purchasing.

The Fiamma Volkswagen T5 Bike Rack bike carrier has been specially designed for Volkswagen T5 Campervans and Minivans which have a single rear door. Easy to install with the standard brackets supplied.
This Fiamma bike rack is suitable for the VW California, VW Transporter and VW Multivan registered after 07/2003. The T5 Bike Carry Rack easily hooks under and over the rear tailgate without the need to drill.   • Bike-Block Pro 1 and and D2 (frame to bike holder)

  • TÜV approved

Product Description:
Dometic NRX80 Compressor 12/24 Volt Motorhome & Caravan Fridge Freezer 

This 75 Litre Compressor 12/24 Volt Fridge Freezer is perfect for caravans, motorhomes, boats and campervans

The new compressor fridge with a completely removable freezer compartment, can create a full fridge space when needed. The Dometic technology has added benefits of low energy consumption, this means that it can easily run in conjunction with solar panels. The NRX80 has a 75 Litre capacity and has a layer of polyurethane insulation to maintain the cool temperatures inside. With the low energy consumption combined with the polyurethane insulation make for a great combination of efficiency and economy.

This 75 litre capacity NRX80 fridge, and a 6.6 litre freezer has a completely removable freezer compartment, which unlike like the previous model, means that you can fully utilise the fridge area if you have no need for the freezer. As a result of this, you can use the Dometic NRX80 compressor fridge as a conventional fridge/freezer, a full fridge or even a full freezer (down to -6°C) in your motorhome or caravan, boat or campervan.

Dometic NRX80 Motorhome & Caravan Compressor Fridge Freezer Features:

  • 3 in 1 solution with unique removable freezer compartment: cooling, freezing or both at the same time.
  • Intelligent electronic control of the compressor speed - up to 25% less energy consumption
  • Integral unique on/off button on the internal control panel
  • Condensed drainage via hose connection, if required, as standard
  • Automatic reverse pole connection
  • Fully hermetic compressor with integrated control electronics
  • Fan speed automatically adjusts to the ambient temperature
  • Perfect temperature control due to new design soft touch panel
  • Bright LED interior lights with infrared on/off sensor
  • Door lock with dual function, lock or vent
  • Stainless steel look door

The MAXVIEW Target range of fully atomatic satellite systems come in dish sizes of 65cm or 85cm with either a single or a twin LNB option.

Product Name: Dometic Cool-Ice WCI 13 Portable Coolbox
Product Description:
The Dometic Cool Ice WCI13 CoolBox

The Dometic Cool-ice WCI13 cool box is designed to keep ice for anything up to 10 days depending on model usage and conditions that it’s used in. Popular for weekend getaways and camping trips and robust enough to deal with the continuous exposure to weather experienced on boats, the WCI13 is a robust all rounder.

With impact resistant, seamless moulded plastic, this Dometic coolbox boasts "indestructible" durability with a unique seal design to ensure superior ice storage. With food grade polyethylene construction and refrigeration grade foam insulation the Dometic WCI 13 is hygienic and easy to clean with high efficiency rating.

Dometic Cool Ice WCI-13 CoolBox Key Features

  • Low heat absorption
  • Seamless casing
  • Highly durable construction for the toughest conditions
  • Melt water drain plug
  • Stainless Steel Rod Hinges
  • Strong nylon latches for easy lock and seal
  • Large none slip feet
  • Keeps ice frozen for several days
  • Food grade polyethylene CFC free material
  • Durable, hygienic and easy to clean
  • High efficiency rating
  • Handy shoulder strap included
  • Available in a range of colours

Best Usage Tips:

  • Chill all groceries and drinks before use and pack the boxes as full as possible (standard freezer packs or ice cubes are suitable as coolants).
  • Store the ice box in a cool area for several hours before and during use, making sure to keep it out of direct sunlight.
  • Please avoid opening the coolbox unnecessarily as air will compromise the cooling capacity and limit the cooling duration.
  • Ambient temperatures play a huge part in the capacity to keep ice for longer, so please be aware that the maximum time given for keeping ice can vary due to this.

Product Name: Certikin Hurricane Commercial Swimming Pool Pumps
Product Description:
Certikin Hurricane Commercial Pumps

The Certikin Hurricane commercial swimming pool pump range offers all the power and performance of a traditional cast iron centrifugal pump with the added versatility of a chemically resistant and is built with lightweight modern plastic in design. The Certikin Hurricane isn't just a pump; it's a powerhouse designed to tackle the demanding needs of large-scale commercial pools and water features. Its robust construction and high-flow performance along with unwavering reliability make it the ideal choice for hotels, resorts, aquatic centres, and any application where clear water and efficient circulation are crucial. 

The Certikin Hurricane pump is capable of pumping large volumes of water at high pressure, the Hurricane pumps are also supplied with 3- phase motors starting at 2.9 kW (4.0HP) through to 9.2kW (12.5HP), achieving flows in excess of 150m3/ hr.

Features:

  • Flooded suction: Unlike traditional pumps that require water to be above a certain level to function, the Certikin Hurricane has a flooded suction design. This means it can effortlessly prime and maintain optimal performance even at lower water levels, making it ideal for pools with variable water depths or those with automatic pool covers.
  • Saltwater compatible: Traditional pool pumps can be easily corroded by the harsh chemicals in saltwater pools. The Certikin Hurricane, however, is built with saltwater-resistant materials, such as 316 stainless steel and bronze impellers, to withstand the corrosive nature of saltwater and provide long-lasting durability. This makes it the perfect choice for saltwater pools, spas, and other marine environments.
  • Pre-filter versatility: The Certikin Hurricane comes in two models: with or without a pre-filter. The pre-filter model is ideal for pools with a lot of debris, as it captures large particles before they reach the pump, protecting it from damage and extending its lifespan. The non-pre-filter model is a good option for pools with minimal debris or those that already have a separate filtration system.
  • Quick fit unions: Installing and maintaining a pool pump can be a time-consuming and frustrating task. The Certikin Hurricane features quick-fit union connections that make it easy to connect and disconnect the pump from the plumbing system. This saves you time and effort, and makes routine maintenance a easier and quicker.

Built to Last:

  • 316 stainless steel shaft: Resists corrosion and wear for exceptional longevity.
  • High-performance impellers: Choose from plastic (4.0HP and 5.5HP) or bronze (7.5HP, 10HP, and 12.5HP) impellers for optimal flow and efficiency.
  • Stainless steel strainer basket (pre-filter models): Captures debris and protects your pump, ensuring smooth operation.
  • IP55 protection: Provides exceptional resistance to dust and water ingress for enhanced safety and reliability.
  • Max water temperature of 40°C: Suitable for a wide range of pool environments and applications.

Product Name: Endless Pools Fastlane Swimming Pool Counter Current Unit
Product Description:
Endless Pools Fastlane Swimming Pool Counter Current Unit

If your pool is too short for a good swim the Endless Pools Fastlane Swimming Pool Counter Current Unit provides a perfect solution and lets you swim for as long as you like without turning. The Fastlane counter current unit can be adjusted easily to your pace by using the supplied remote control so you can enjoy swimming in a smooth, even current like swimming in a river.

There are two types of Endless Pools Fastlane Swimming Pool Counter Current Unit, a 'Deck Mount' unit for retrofitting in existing pools and an 'In Wall' version for new build or refurbishments.

Easy installation and maintenance as the Fastlane counter current unit can be rolled across the pool deck and dropped into the water. Simple hydraulics mean no electrical connections poolside.

Swimmers love the quality of the adjustable speed of the swim current - children love it because it's just plain fun. A Fastlane transforms your pool into a water park.

 

Endless Pools Fastlane Counter Current Unit Features

  • Can be fitted to almost any pool.
  • Minimum water depth required is 35".
  • 16" propeller.
  • Supplied with 1 remote control fob.
  • Adjustable speed setting suitable for all swimming levels.
  • Ideal exercise, therapy and fun. 
  • 5HP power unit can be placed up to 200'/60 metres away.
  • Endless Pools Fastlane can be fitted to virtually any pool either new build or retrofit with a minimum 35" water depth required.
  • A 5HP pump with a 16" diameter propeller gives a maximum 66 second 100 yard pace.
  • 2 Year Warranty

 

How the Fastlane Counter Current Unit Works

Easy to install with no electrical connections poolside, the Fastlane can be installed in virtually any pool, including new or existing in-ground concrete, vinyl-lined, or fibreglass pools and in many above ground pools. The Swim Unit can be placed in water as shallow as 89cm. Generally if the pool is deep enough for swimming, it's deep enough for a Fastlane system.

The Endless Pools Fastlane Swimming Pool Counter Current Unit comprises of a remotely located Hydraulic Power Unit that powers the Swim Unit that mounts poolside. These components are connected by two hydraulic hoses designed to keep electricity well away from the water. The poolside Swim Unit includes a submerged hydraulic motor that turns the custom-designed 40.6cm propeller with an innovative channelling system to straighten the water flow into a smooth swim current.

The rugged 5-hp Power Unit is typically located with your other pool plant, keeping any electricity away from the pool. The remote Power Unit contains 19 litres of biodegradable vegetable-based hydraulic fluid that is pumped to the Swim Unit. With the push of a button, you can vary the flow of oil to change the speed of the propeller and thus the swim current.

Deck Mounted Endless Pools Fastlane Counter Current

 

 

 The Deck Mount Fastlane enables retrofitting to an existing pool. The Fastlane hangs over the pool wall and is held in place by a deck plate bolted to the pool deck. The hydraulic hoses run up and over the coping beneath the Deck Mount Cover.

  1. Swim Unit
  2. Intake Grill
  3. Outlet Grill
  4. Stainless Steel Grab Bar
  5. Deck Mount Bracket
  6. Hydraulic Hose System
  7. Power Unit

 

Wall Mounted Endless Pools Fastlane Counter Current

 

The Wall Mount Fastlane anchors directly to the pool wall at the waterline making this model suitable for new construction or major pool renovations. All connections and hoses remain out of sight, beneath the pool deck.

  1. Swim Unit
  2. Intake Grill
  3. Outlet Grill

Certikin Swimming Pool Counter Current Unit
Product Description:
Certikin Swimming Pool Counter Current Unit

The Certikin Swimming Pool Counter Current Unit is specially designed with small pools in mind to give you a new way to enjoy your pool and exercise at the same time. Installing a Certikin Counter Current unit in your pool enables you to swim as far as you like without the need for turning around.

The Counter Current system is equiped with a 3HP Certikin pump to provide a constant stream of water which enables you to swim on the spot. The current flow is adjustable so swimmers of all abilites can swim at their own pace as long as they like in your own pool.

A directional outlet on the Certikin Counter Current Unit allows a 15 degree inclination in any direction and also featuers an adjustable air/water mixer for a relaxing bubble massage effect.

 

What's Included with the Certikin Swimming Pool Counter Current Unit:

  • Faceplate assembly and housing with jet
  • On / off controls
  • 3 HP pump (1 or 3 phase) with connection accessories (2x elbows, 2x valves - pipework not included)
  • Control box to activate the pump via faceplate controls
  • Air suction connection 20mm diameter with air button and flexible pipe
  • Directional inlet 41mm diameter which provides water and air regulation and up to 15 degrees movement

 

Installation of your Certikin Counter Current Unit

The counter current unit housing should be installed during swimming pool construction. The Certikin swimming pool counter current unit can be purchased in component form as follows:

  1. Faceplate assembly and housing
  2. Pump kit
  3. Control box

Only the Counter Current unit Faceplate assembly and housing is required at pool construction phase this enables pool construction at relatively low cost and allows full installation of the system at a later date if required. The pump should be installed as close as possible to the pool for maximum performance (within wiring regulations).

Thetford T1090E 90L Caravan Motorhome Compressor Fridge (Curved Rear)
Product Description:
Thetford T1090E 12v Compressor fridge (Replaces T2090)

Curved back for a snug fit

This compressor fridge is specifically designed for use in panel van conversions, allowing for the curvature of the wall. The compact measurements of this 12v fridge give you more freedom with your campervan, caravan or motorhome's internal layout, allowing for the curvature of your vehicle's walls.

High-tech compressor performance

Thetford have expanded on the already-popular performance of the T1090, finding big efficiency gains with the T1090E (replaces T2090). The fridge's battery efficiency gives you an incredible 8 days (on 2 x 95 Ah batteries), making it perfect for extended off-grid trips. The display is a LED panel, allowing you to easily switch between operating modes. The Thetford T1090E, for example, includes a Night Mode function, which reduces the noise of the fridge to a whisper, letting you get a good night's sleep. These features can also be controlled via the latest campervan, motorhome and caravan control panels, thanks to the inclusion of CI-BUS compatibility.

Versatile cooling

The Thetford T1090E compressor fridge includes an integrated 6 litre freezer compartment, ensuring you aren't limited in the food you bring on your journey. This freezer space, combined with an additional 78 litres of fridge space, ensures you won't feel compromised on the road. You can even use the touch panel to disable the fridge freezer if you wish, allowing you to save power.

Key Features: 

  • No external vent required 
  • Unique shape allows for the curve on the wall of your van 
  • Ultra efficient power use
  • Day & night mode makes it super efficient 
  • 90 litre capacity with compact dimensions 
  • Low noise operation
  • Freezer to minus 9 degrees

Product Name: Astral Vic Bobbin Wound Commercial Swimming Pool Sand Filter
Product Description:
Astral Vic Commercial Bobbin Wound Swimming Pool Sand Filter

The Astral Vic bobbin wound filter provides a high quality and robust filtration solution for commercial swimming pools and replaces the Atena model. Featuring a new top cover system with quick locking mechanism and a 400 x 500 mm opening. The air relief valve is fitted into the cover in order to help eliminate air from the filter.
 
The Vic bobbin wound commercial filter is fitted with new 1 1/2" collector arms in moulded ABS, these one piece laterals vary in length from 90mm to 525mm and replace the need for interconnecting unions previously required to make up the length. This makes maintenance easier and more effective. Less head drain loss is also achieved thanks to the increased diameter of the collector arms.

The collector tubes are manufactured in moulded PVC and have a diameter of 90mm. Water drainage and air relief are now quicker thanks to the inclusion of 1" diameter air and water purge valves.

The distance between the upper sand bed and the freeboard has been increased to ensure improved water distribution in the filtration stage and to avoid sand falling into the drainage system during the wash cycle.

These Astral Vic commercial bobbin wound swimming pool filters are suitable for filtration velocities of 20, 30 & 40m³/h/m² and feature a 1.0m deep filtration bed.

All Astral Vic filters are designed to be connected to Valve manifolds bought separately.

If ozone is to be used an interior vinylester coating is required.

Maximum working pressure for all Astral Vic commercial bobbin wound swimming pool filters is 2.5 Kg/cm²

Filter vessels with 2000mm diameter may require a special transport vehicle. Please ask at time of ordering.

Maxview VuQube 2 Caravan Motorhome Portable Automatic Satellite System
Product Description:
The Maxview VuQube 2 Fully Automatic Portable Satellite System

The VuQube 2 is a fully enclosed automatic satellite system designed to receive satellite TV and radio in the UK and Europe at the press of a button, using a wired control box.

Compact and easily portable, the Maxview VuQube 2 Automatic Satellite Dish for Caravans and Motorhomes is self levelling on uneven or sloping surfaces and is compatible with all UK satellite receivers.

Fully automatic, the Maxview VuQube 2 Portable Satellite System will do all the hard work for you whilst you get on with other things.

Simply select the satellite that you want and let it do its thing!

Featuring an easy to use LED control box, a strong, weather resistant casing and ergonomically designed handle, the lightweight Maxview VuQube 2 Portable Satellite System is incredibly user friendly, convenient and optimised for easy mobility and sustained performance.

Please Note: That this system does NOT include a satellite receiver- please see the related products section for information on our range of satellite receiver options.

Maxview VuQube 2 Features:

  • Twin LNB as Standard. For use with PVR’s, SKY+ or 2 receivers in different locations
  • Includes Velcro to mount control box conveniently inside a cupboard
  • Designed and tested for outdoor use
  • High quality, durable and robust construction
  • 2 year guarantee

Product Name: Certikin Wide Mouth Swimming Pool Skimmer
Product Description:
Certikin Wide Mouth Swimming Pool Skimmer

The Certikin Swimming Pool Skimmer HD100SN with wide angled extension is designed to extract water from the surface of the pool and efficiently remove any floating debris, leaves etc. The Skimmer retains any debris collected and thus prevents it sinking to the bottom of the swimming pool.

The Wide angled extension throat  has two variants which dictates the use for either concrete or liner pool installation.

The Certikin Wide Mouth Swimming Pool Skimmer is supplied with a collar weir for quiet and reliable operation.

Certikin Swimming Pool Skimmer Features:

  • Robust one-piece body reduces the risk of water loss from the pool.
  • Overflow and water fill outlets provided.
  • Outlet connections in imperial and metric.
  • Extending collar and square lid for ease of installation.
  • Extension throats allow the skimmer body to be positioned ANY DISTANCE from the pool wall - ideal when using an automatic pool cover or when designing a pool with an ornate surround.
  • Max flow rate 4.5m³ per hour

Please use the drop down menu at the top of the page to confirm your choice of Certikin Wide Mouth Swimming Pool Skimmer and accessories.

Certikin 1.5" Wall Inlets For Concrete Swimming Pool
Product Description:
Certikin 1.5" Wall Inlets For Concrete Swimming Pool

The Certikin Wall Inlets for use with a Concrete Swimming Pool are available in two types; the Eyeball inlet and the Fixed Grate inlet with a maximum flow rate of 5m³/hour.

Eyeball Wall Inlet-

The Certikin Eyeball wall inlet HD53C for concrete pools enables the direction of flow into the pool to be easily controlled by adjustment of the 'Eyeball'. This features a safety grille to prevent children's prying fingers. By adjusting the flow direction pool heating and chemical dispersion is made easier.

Fixed Grate Inlet-

The Certikin Fixed Grate inlet HD54C for concrete pools is used where an automatic pool cleaner or vacuum hose is to be fitted. The vacuum point can be plumbed in for use either as a suction point or return fitting.

Both inlets are available with plumbed pipe approx 550mm/22" long.

All are manufactured from ABS for durability and for 1.5" fittings.

Product Description:

Certikin 6" Swimming Pool Main Drain Features:

  • Protective film prevents installation damage

Maximum flow rate for the Certikin 6" Swimming pool main drain is 4.5m³/hour with 1.5" connection and 9.5m³/hour with 2" connection.

Project 2000 Manual/Electronic Caravan Campervan and Motorhome Motorised Step
Product Description:
The Project 2000 M440/480 Step for Motorhome, Campervan, and Caravan

M440 Manual Caravan Campervan Step

Features:

  • New structure is made from both steel and aluminium and is designed to grant higher stability.
  • Strong protection against salty fog on the steel parts through galvanization and epoxy paint.
  • Manual step operation
  • Quick movement on brass bushes able to grant smooth movement over time.
  • Footboard is from anodised aluminium with anti-slip rubber, to facilitate safe entry to your Campervan Motorhome or caravan
  • Step tread width is 440mm.
  • Weight: 4.2KG.
  • Manual release system for emergencies

The Project 2000 range of step are designed for use with most Caravan, Campervan and Motorhome. Easy to install, the manual M440 and M480 model listed here is operated by Simply pulling the step from it's secure housing and stowing away again when your campervan caravan motorhome is ready to relocate. The M440 makes for an easy, cost effective, and dignified entry into your Campervan, Caravan or Motorhome, and folds away neatly into its weatherproof housing beneath your Camper, caravan or motorhome. The Project 2000 M440 is the most cost effective manual option for your motorhome, caravan or campervan, in the project 2000 range.

M480 Electronic Caravan Campervan Step

The M480 is the electronic version of the step, and is operated by a switch inside the motorhome campervan or caravan, that should be conveniently situated for easy reach when the habitation door is open.

Features:

  • Anti-shock clutch able to preserver the motor and gearbox from violent hits while the step is in motion.
  • Manual step release system for emergency without having to disconnect any mechanical component.
  • High power engine, working on ball bearings, with thermal breaker in case of excessive strain.
  • Strong protection against salty fog of the steel parts through galvanization and epoxy paint.
  • Opening and closing with manned operation until completely closed/opened.
  • Quick movement on brass bushes able to grant smooth movement over time.
  • Water proof sensor for "open step" warning light integrated in motor carter.
  • High motion speed: step open to step close in 1.5 seconds.
  • Step footboard is from anodised aluminium with anti-slip rubber, to facilitate safe entry to your Campervan Motorhome or Caravan
  • Energy input: 3A.
  • Weight 8KG.

Commercial Swimming Pool Pump Variable Speed Drive Inverter

This commercial swimming pool pump variable speed drive inverter is easy to install and programme. The variable speed drive can be used with a wide range of pumps and is suitable for connection to a Building Management System (BMS)  By reducing the running speed of the swimming pool pump the variable speed drive can deliver substantial energy savings and a reduction of pump noise. During backwashing or if higher flow rates are required the pump can be run at 100% speed.

Commercial Swimming Pool Pump Variable Speed Drive Inverter Features:

  • Easy to install and programme

  • IP66 rated
  • Operating conditions up to 50° Centigrade

The commercial variable speed drive inverter is suitable for use with various pump models including: BP Range, BHP Range, Calpeda, Modern, Hurricane, Giant, Great Giant, Hydrostar, Columbia, Victoria, Aral, Maxim, Shark, Speck, Hayward, Waterco, Starite and DAB

Product Name: Zodiac pH Expert Swimming Pool Automatic pH Regulator
Product Description:
Zodiac pH Expert Swimming Pool Automatic pH Regulator

The Zodiac pH Expert swimming pool regulator provides automatic pH regulation for all types of in-ground pools up to 150m³ and can be installed in either an existing or a new build swimming pool. 

Advantages of the Zodiac pH Expert Swimming Pool Automatic pH Regulator:

  • Simple to use - with values easily set on the LCD screen of the Zodiac pH Expert regulator.
  • Automatic pH Dosage - It is vital to have a stable and correct pH in the swimming pool for effective operation of the oxidant (usually chlorine). Maintaining the correct pH of the pool the Zodiac pH Expert regulator ensures savings in oxidant use and prevents potential problems of eye irritation, corrosion of coatings and algae development.  The pH Expert regulator continually measures the pH of the swimming pool water and automatically adjusts the pH if required.
  • Accurate adjustments - the Zodiac pH Expert Automatic swimming pool regulator injects a precise amount of pH corrector with an adaptive dosing technology to ensure perfect water balance with minimum amount of product. The dosing time is adjusted automatically depending on the difference between the measured pH of the swimming pool and the required ideal value.
  • Anti Overdose protection - the Zodiac pH Expert automatic pH regulator guards against risk of pH corrector overdosing thanks to its exclusive safety system to ensure optimal water balance. Safe dosing of the swimming pool is enhanced with the unique suction tube.
  • Water Alkalinity Compensation (TAC) - the Zodiac pH expert ensures optimal use of pH corrector by use of a function to adjust the treatment cycle depending on the swimming pool water alkalinity (TAC) level.

The Zodiac pH Expert swimming pool automatic regulator is supplied with probes and all installation fittings except the chemical holding tanks.
Product Availability: Delivery of the Zodiac pH Expert swimming pool automatic regulator is 2/3 working days!

Product Description:
Thetford N4104 Motorhome Campervan and Caravan Absorption Fridge

The Thetford N4104 Motorhome Campervan and Caravan Fridge is a new compact 3 way absorption fridge featuring an improved, accommodating freezer with quality assured build for reliability and longevity.

With it’s 105 litre capacity (inclusive of an 11 litre freezer compartment), the Thetford N4104 Motorhome Campervan and Caravan Fridge is perfect for keeping treats and essentials cool and secure whilst on the go, and also comes supplied with flexible shelving, door bins and a bottle slide to ensure that your goods remain stable whilst your caravan, motorhome or campervan is in transit.

Featuring an easy to use control panel, and with electric ignition, the Thetford N4104 Motorhome Campervan and Caravan Fridge is guaranteed to deliver an unparalleled cooling performance with low key, quiet operations so you’ll barely even hear it working. Additionally, the automatic version of the Thetford N4104 is available as a framed or frameless variant.

The A model fridges are also fully automatic, and features an advanced LCD control panel for easier diagnostics and control.

Product Name: Thetford C223S Caravan & Motorhome Cassette Toilet
Product Description:
Thetford C223S Caravan and Motorhome Cassette Toilet

A high quality Cassette Toilet for use in caravan, campervan or motorhome with their own onboard water tank, the Thetford C223S Cassette Toilet features a waste tank capacity of 18 litres and comes with the convenience of electric flush.

The built-in Cassette Toilet consists of two parts: a permanently installed toilet and a removable waste-holding tank. A useful indicator lets you know when the tank needs to be emptied, and you can access and remove the tank through a small door on the outside of the motorhome, campervan or caravan.

This terrific caravan and motorhome toilet from Thetford is suitable for installation against the external side wall or rear wall of the caravan, motorhome or campervan but can also be easily installed against an interior wall in your vehicle/vessel, provided there is level access on the other side, to enable the waste tank removal.

The Thetford C223S Cassette Toilet also benefits from a fully adjustable swivel seat / bowl which can be moved through 180 degrees to accommodate for installation and positioning in tight, awkward spaces in your caravan, campervan or motorhome.

Thetford C223S Caravan and Motorhome Cassette Toilet Features:

  • Highest level of seating comfort on the market
  • Lightweight, high-quality, durable white plastic
  • Quiet yet powerful flushing system with full bowl coverage - 12V Electric
  • 3 year warranty
  • Waste-holding tank indicates when it needs emptying
  • Waste-holding tank on wheels
  • Vent button for emptying without splashing
  • Automatic pressure release vent prevents gas build-up, ensures splash-free tank opening
  • Built-in rotating spout for emptying
  • Waste tank capacity: 18L
  • Flush water tank capacity: Dependent upon vehicle’s central water tank.
  • Dimensions: H495 x W365 x D580mm
  • An electric flush button control that can be mounted away from the toilet
  • **Please Note** This product usually requires the purchase of the Thetford 'Access Door' This provides neat access for removal of the waste tank.

What’s the difference between a CS & S?

The latest versions of the C220 and C260 Thetford Cassette toilets come with two designs, a CS and S but what’s the difference?

Product Name: Vango Tailgate Hub II Low Driveaway Campervan Awning
Product Description:
Vango Tailgate Hub II Low Driveaway Campervan Awning

Versatile driveaway awning for the vehicle rear or side

The Vango Tailgate Hub II Low is a tailgate awning designed for campervans and SUVs, ideal for couples and solo travellers. Attachment requires only pegging straps at the front of the vehicle and tunnel area, allowing the awning to fit neatly to your vehicle without the need for kador rails. However, should you wish to use them, the traditional attachment options of roof bar attachment tabs, kador and a sleeve for pole and clamp are also included. Roll away the connecting tunnel when not in use to allow you to drive away for the day (drive-away kit needed for kador fittting) the awning does not require the tailgate to be open to support the structure.

Features include flat entry doors for easy access for wheelchairs or prams, an internal mesh bug screen on the front door, and a linked-in removable groundsheet. The large diamond-clear windows allow for ample light to fill the living area, and they have roll-away curtains for privacy. The roll away tunnel has two doors for easy access to the front and back of your vehicle. The awning packs neatly away into the provided carry bag.

Vango Tailgate Hub II Low Features:

  • Sentinel Active 75D is lightweight, compact and waterproof with an HH rating of 3,000MM.
  • Flat entry to doors provides easy access to prams or wheelchairs. 
  • Internal mesh bug screen on the front door.
  • Diamond clear windows maximise natural light, with toggled privacy curtains.
  • Two doors in tunnel attachment.
  • Roll-away connecting tunnel allows you to drive away for the day, leaving the awning standing (use a drive-away kit to easily detach the tunnel area)
  • Vango's SkyTrack II is a flexible hanging system which allows you to easily attach lighting or storage.
  • Lantern hanging points.
  • Carry bag included.
  • Steel pegs included.
  • Fully wind and rain tested to the European standard EN5912.
  • Linked-In groundsheet can be attached or detached from the living area when not needed.
  • High visibility guylines.
  • Can be pitched on the side or rear of your campervan.
  • Attaches to a range of vehicles with heights ranging from 120cm-190cm.

Hub II Low Specification:

  • Weight: 11.4kg
  • Depth: 250.0cm
  • Height: 215.0cm
  • Width: 250.0cm
  • Pitching Time: 8mins
  • Kador Length: 210cm
  • Kador Height: 180-210 (Low)cm
  • Fabric: Sentinel A
  • Connection Width: 190cm
  • Pack Size (Bag 1): L70cm x H28cm x W30cm
  • Bag 1 Weight: 10.4kg
  • Rail Weight: 5.6kg
Product Warranty: The Vango Tailgate Hub II Low awning comes with a two year warranty from the date of purchase. Register your new awning with Vango online to extend it to three years.

Product Name: Dometic-Smev 9722 Caravan Motorhome Sink & 2 burner Hob Combination Unit
Product Description:
Dometic Smev 9722 Caravan and Motorhome Sink and 2 Burner Hob Combination Unit

The Dometic Smev 9722 sink and hob combination unit provides a stylish and compact solution for caravan and motorhome making the most out of minimal space. With a double burner hob and the option of having the sink on the right or left this versatile combination unit is finished with heat resistant glass lids which can be used as an extra work surface when the Dometic Smev 9722 hob is not in use.

Siphon and seal included

Piezo ignition and easy cleaning

Fitted with a Piezo ignition system the Dometic Smev 9722 caravan and motorhome sink and hob combination unit also comes with detachable pan supports and enamelled burner caps for ease of use and cleaning.

Safety Ignition System

A flame failure device is included for peace of mind that the gas will shut off if the flame is extinguished unexpectedly. The Dometic 9722 is available in 12v or piezo ignition.

Left or right?

Please note left or right hand is reflective of the side the sink sits on as you look at it.

Optional tap

Please note that the Dometic Smev 9722 caravan and motorhome sink and hob combination unit is not supplied with a tap but to order a folding tap alongside the purchase of the Dometic Smev 9722 simply tick which tap either cold or a mixer tap you would like before adding your purchase to the shopping cart. This tap will have barbed tails.

Please note, Dometic warranty does not cover 9722 hobs for boat and marine usage, including both inland and offshore waterways.

Feelfree Nomad Sport Sit On Top Kayak With Wheel
Product Description:
Feelfree Nomad Sport Sit On Top Kayak With Wheel

The Feelfree Nomad Sport is a great solo sit on top kayak suitable for whole family use and designed for stability yet still maneuverable. This Nomad Sport kayak is manufactured to a high standard being a robust and durable design featuring moulded carry handles on the sides, bow and stern, with a handy centre storage hatch and space for fitting fishing rod holders. The wheel  built in to the keel enables easy movement of the Feelfree Nomad Sport Kayak on hard surfaces.

The Feelfree Nomad Sport is a Great all round Kayak

The Feelfree Nomad sit on top Kayak is suitable for general use on lakes, canals, gently moving rivers, sheltered coastal areas and in small surf. This stable, straight tracking and maneuverable kayak is also great for kayak fishing. The Feelfree Nomad Sport Sit On Top Kayak has a self bailing seating area so that water splashing over will drain away and is comfortable to paddle especially when a padded seat is used for extra back support.

Feelfree Juntos Sit On Top Kayak
Product Description:
Feelfree Juntos Sit On Top Kayak

The Feelfree Juntos is a solo sit-on-top kayak that will also take a child passenger on board – the perfect 1 + ½ kayak. It is the ideal solution for those wanting a solo kayak that they can handle and paddle well on their own with a bit of extra storage space, yet will comfortably take a small passenger (or pet). A child-size seat pad is positioned towards the bow of the kayak enabling both paddler and child to face each other as the Feelfree Juntos kayak moves through the water.

 

The Feelfree Juntos is a general purpose adult sit on top kayak with an additional child seat at the front

With stability and easy straight line tracking the Feelfree Juntos sit on kayak is a great general purpose kayak perfect for recreational family use. The Juntos sit on top kayak has a large rear storage well and a storage hatch in the centre of the kayak. For easy handling the Feelfree Juntos sit on kayak has moulded-in front, rear & side handles as well as a wheel in the keel for moving the Juntos on hard surfaces.

 

Feelfree Juntos Sit On Kayak Features:

 

  • Front seat for a child or pet
  • Centre hatch with mesh bag
  • Large rear tankwell with bungee
  • Moulded carry handles at the front, back and sides
  • Drinks bottle holder
  • Wheel In The Keel
  • Seat (optional Extra)
  • Rod holders (Optional Extra)

Feelfree Gemini  Sport Tandem Sit On Top Kayak

The Feelfree Gemini Sport Tandem Kayak is a stable and easy to paddle double Sit On Top Kayak. The versatile Feelfree Gemini Sport can be paddled as a solo, a tandem or a tandem with a smaller child in the middle.This Gemini Sport kayak is manufactured to a high standard being a robust and durable design featuring moulded carry handles on the sides, bow and stern, with two handy storage hatches and space for fitting fishing rod holders. The wheel  built in to the keel enables easy movement of the Feelfree Gemini Sport Kayak on hard surfaces.

The Feelfree Gemini Sport is a Great all round Kayak

The Feelfree Gemini Sport Tandem sit on top Kayak is suitable for general use on lakes, canals, gently moving rivers, sheltered coastal areas. This stable Gemini Sport Sit On Top Kayak has a self bailing seating area so that water splashing over will drain away and is comfortable to paddle especially when a padded seat is used for extra back support.  An optional directional skeg can also be fitted to assist paddlers in keeping straight which needs removal for solo paddlers.

Feelfree Move Sit On Top Kayak
Product Description:
Feelfree Move Sit On Top Kayak

The Feelfree Move Sit On Top Kayak is a compact general purpose kayak to suit smaller adults and children. With a wide hull the stable Feelfree Move is easy to paddle and the defined keel helps with straight line tracking. This Sit On Top Kayak is suited to paddling  on canals, lakes, slow flowing rivers and calm coastal waters.

The Feelfree Move is Stable General Purpose Kayak

A robust, well designed and compact sit on top kayak the general purpose Feelfree Move has moulded bow, stern and side handles, bow hatch, rear tank well, drain plug and wheel in the keel. The wheel in the keel is designed for use on harder surfaces, not very rough ground,  soft sand or mud. The Feelfree Move is a great all round sit on top kayak for smaller paddlers looking for a smaller kayak or introduction to kayaking.

 Feelfree Move Sit On Top Kayak Features:

  • Drinking bottle holder.
  • Front Storage hatch.
  • Wheel built into the keel
  • Bow, stern and side handles.
  • Rear tank well bungee cords
  • Optional thigh strap mounts
  • MDPE (Medium Density Polyethylene)
  • Seat (Optional Extra)
  • Rod holders (Optional Extra)

Feelfree Corona Sit On Top Kayak
Product Description:
Feelfree Corona Sit On Top Kayak

The Feelfree Corona is the ultimate three person sit on top kayak ideal for touring and family use. With a higher carrying capacity than most other tandem kayaks the Feelfree Corona will easily accommodate two adults plus a larger child and equipment. Even with three people the Corona sit on top kayak is stable and easy to paddle. The Corona is also a popular option for two person paddling where more storage space and capacity is required, larger paddlers or going off camping.

Feelfree Corona is a Large Capacity Versatile Kayak

For ease of use the Feelfree Corona sit on top kayak has 4 moulded handles, a rear storage well with bungee's, front gear bungee's, 2 storage hatches, 2 paddle parks and multiple equipment attachment points.  The Corona kayak also features a 'wheel in the keel' to enable easy transport on hard surfaces like slipways. For solo use the Feelfree Corona kayak can be paddled from the centre position.

When this kayak is used by three people it is recommended that two people paddle, with the third person as a passenger, to avoid clashing of paddles.

Product Description:
Feelfree Windermere Sit Inside Recreational Touring and Fishing Kayak

Feelfree are well established wordwide for excellent sit on top recreational and fishing kayaks - they also produce versatile sit inside recreational touring and fishing kayaks. The Windermere sit inside kayak is an easy to paddle kayak from Feelfree designed for recreational touring and fishing.  The Feelfree Windermere has been a best seller in the USA for many years and is now available in the UK.

 

Feelfree Windermere Is An Easy To Use Sit Inside Kayak

The Feelfree Windermere  is designed for easy paddling in canals, estuaries, lakes and sheltered waters. With a large open cockpit for easy access the Feelfree Windermere is a great kayak for paddlers wanting to  move from a sit on top to a sit inside kayak. With recreational use in mind the Feelfree Windermere sit inside kayak features a comfortable seat, adjustable foot rests, a pair of fishing rod holders, rear storage pod, deck elastics, thigh pads, drain plug and carry handles.

  • Two fishing rod holders with leashes
  • Thigh pads
  • Adjustable footrests

  • Adjustable backrest

  • Built in front console

Electronic Pool Cleaner

The Dolphin M250 is designed to offer effective and affordable cleaning for your swimming pool. This reliable and easy-to-use robotic cleaner is ideal for pools up to 10 meters (33 ft) in length, including beach-entry pools. With a 2-hour cleaning cycle and advanced features like a swivel cable to prevent tangling and dual brushing technology, the Dolphin M250 makes pool maintenance hassle-free. It includes a self-contained filter bag or cartridge to collect dirt and debris, reducing the need for backwashing and saving both water and energy. Product Name: Dolphin Supreme M400 Pro Automatic Swimming Pool Cleaner
Product Description:
Dolphin Supreme M400 Pro Automatic Swimming Pool Cleaner

The Dolphin Supreme M400 Pro robotic pool cleaner provides reliable and efficient cleaning of swimming pools up to 12m (40ft). This automatic pool cleaner thoroughly cleans the floor, walls and water line of the swimming pool and leaves the water sparkling clean in 2.5 hours without manual intervention and with minimal cost. The Dolphin Supreme M400 Pro Automatic swimming pool cleaner is equipped with standard brushes with the optional extra of 'wonder brushes' for tiled pools. Supplied with a caddy for easy handling the Dolphin M400 Pro Electronic has 18 meters of cable with a swivel to avoid cable tangles.

Please note that wonder brushes are recommended for tiled pools and can be purchased separately above.

Dolphin Supreme M400 Pro Automatic Swimming Pool Cleaner Benefits & Features:

  • Brushes, scrubs, vacuums, and filters the entire swimming pool including the floor, walls and waterline.
  • Top opening filtration compartments for easy and convenient maintenance.
  • Swivel on cable prevents cable tangling.
  • Integrated gyro further enhances scanning efficiency, precision and maneuverability.
  • Dual-level filtration system, Ultra-fine and Spring net for all type of dirt and debris, even small particles.
  • One-way water valves prevent the escape of debris and ensure rapid water drainage.
  • Delay mechanism enables the cleaning cycle to be delayed by one or two hours.
  • Clogged filter indicator ensures ongoing cleaning efficiency.
  • Dual drive-motor for optimal pool maneuverability and coverage, regardless of shape, slope and obstacles.
  • Automatic motor protection mechanism.
  • Low voltage, low energy consumption.
  • DIY - Easy maintenance at user and local dealer level.
  • Suitable for beach entry pools.
  • 36 months Warranty on all parts.

Product Description:
The Bestway Lay Z Spa Paris

The 2016 Lay-Z-Spa Paris hot tub is perfect for relaxing and feeling comfortable. The Lay-Z-Spa Paris is the first hot tub to feature stunning multicoloured LED lighting system. Feel rejuvenated with up to 6 people with its excellent massage system and its 87 all surrounding air jets.

Stunning Multicolour LED Lighting System

The Paris inflatable hot tub comes with a stunning Multicolour LED Lighting System which can be changed with a wireless remote to allow you to cycle through 7 colours or have them automatically change. The colours can change from many variations of blue, red, green and more, what ever suits your mood.

Massage System

Feel great with The Lay-Z Paris Spas built in AirJet Massage System. This spa is made up of 87 all surrounding air jets creating a relaxing and rejuvenating bubbles. The Spa also allows the wireless remote to control the pump which can control the massage system.

Rapid Heating System

The Lay-Z Paris comes with a Rapid Heating System that allows the spa to heat up to 40 degrees Celsius. The Spa also includes an insulation, inflatable top lid, an exterior cover with a double lock safety clips and bubble mat, all of this helps to insulate and protect the spa when it is not in use.

Durability

The Paris Spa is designed with a sturdy I-Beam which offers durability and a cushioning structure. This Spa is also weather proof.

Easy to set up!

The Lazy–Z-Spa Paris comes with a useful DVD which contains set-up and maintenance details. You must keep in mind that this spa does not require installation tools. The spa can be inflated using the included air pump/heater and filling the spa with water takes around 10 minutes.
