Compact roof mounted awning designed specifically for campervans

The awning cassette uses automotive industry quality finishing, an aerodynamic design and, along with separately available dedicated brackets, provides a bespoke fitting to a large range of vans and campers.

Why choose the Fiamma F40 VAN Awning?

Compared to conventional motorhome awnings, the Fiamma F40 VAN Awning offers lowered brackets, compact dimensions and a reduced projection, all essential factors for campervan use.

The F40 van low profile adapter brackets are designed to attached to the pre existing fixing points on your campervan or minivan for your convenience and ease of installation and removal without the need to drill into the body work. Each of the Fiamma F40 Van Adapter Brackets are sold separately and vehicle specific, ensuring the right fit to your camper and compatible with Ford Customs, Mercedes Vitos, Renault Trafics and VW T5 & T6 Transporters.

Fiamma F40 VAN Awning Features:

  • Compact Roof Installation with lowered brackets to reduce wind resistance
  • Reinforced arms for stability and confidence
  • Quick to install and uninstall
  • Single guide on the front bar for accessory fitting
  • Flat legs with controlled and predefined opening
  • Available in Deep Black with Royal Grey canopy
  • Reduced height
  • Available in Deep Black with Royal Grey canopy
  • Additional Rain Guard Kit available to improve wind resistance and prevent water ingress between the bracket and vehicle roof

Installation guidance

  • ONLY be installed to standard roof variants
  • If the Campervan is equipped with a C-rail, it is necessary to remove it and locate the brackets in the set points
  • NOT SUITABLE for vehicles with pop tops (including the VW California)
  • Note to customers in Northern Ireland - unfortunately due to shipping costs we cannot fulfil any orders to Northern Ireland. Any orders placed will be refunded.

Product Name: PV Logic 100w Motorhome Caravan Camper Solar Panel Kit Complete
Product Description:
PV Logic 100w Motorhome Caravan Camper Solar Panel Kit Complete

High efficiency 100W solar panel kit, perfect for off-grid campers

The PV Logic 100 watt Solar Panel kit is ideal for use on large sized caravans and motorhomes where the power is used to run the lights, water pump, television, laptop computer etc throughout the year or for extended touring periods. This kit comes complete with universal alloy L brackets, making it easy to install this solar panel kit to campervans and campers. The ever-popular 100W solar kit is capable of supplying up to 650wh a day, allowing it to charge even large leisure batteries.

Optional MPPT Pro charge controller upgrade available

Both the standard and pro charge controllers can charge two 12v or 24v batteries, but the MPPT Pro charge controller offers up to 20% increased solar yields by modifying the panel's voltage to match the batteries' requirements. This allows it to provide better battery charging performance. The MPPT charger also features an Android/Apple smartphone app, allowing you to monitor your solar panel's performance over Bluetooth. Both the standard and MPPT charge controller feature a two-year warranty.

What's in the box?

The kit comprises:

  • 1 x STP100 100 watt solar panel
  • 1 x STCC10 10 amp solar charge controller (Optional MPPT 15 amp smart charge controller also available)
  • 1 x 4 meter cable bundle
  • 1 x FKA08 Standard bracket kit
  • 1 x STMP006 Cable Feed Gland
  • 1 x tube of bonding agent
  • 1 x Pack of fuses, ring terminals etc.
  • 1 x Fitting instructions

PV Logic 100W Solar Panel Kit Features:

  • High-efficiency crystalline solar cells for all-weather charging
  • Built-in diodes prevent battery discharge
  • Tough, robust construction
  • Water resistant for outdoor use
  • 20 year cell performance warranty
  • 10 year module warranty

Product Name: LumiPlus Mini LED Small Swimming Pool Light
Product Description:
LumiPlus Mini LED Swimming Pool Light

Illuminate your pool with the stylish and energy-efficient LumiPlus Mini LED Swimming Pool Light. Designed to deliver exceptional brightness and versatility, this compact light is perfect for enhancing the ambiance of your pool, particularly in areas such as steps or Roman ends. The LumiPlus Mini LED is available in four sleek options to suit your aesthetic preference:

  1. White LED with White Frame
  2. White LED with Stainless Steel Frame
  3. RGB LED with White Frame
  4. RGB LED with Stainless Steel Frame

Unmatched Performance

  • Enhanced Brightness: The LumiPlus Mini V2 LED projectors feature improved light intensity, providing up to 315 lumens for White LED models and 186 lumens for RGB LED models, ensuring your pool is well-lit with vibrant and even illumination.
  • Energy Efficiency: The Mini White Light Projector consumes just 9W, while the RGB version uses only 5.5W, making them highly energy-efficient without compromising on brightness.
  • Versatile Installation: Rated at 12V AC and equipped with a 2.5-meter H07RN-F cable, the LumiPlus Mini LED is designed for easy installation both in and out of water. Its IPX8 protection ensures reliable performance, even under water.

Customizable Ambiance

  • White or RGB Lighting: Choose between a crisp, clear White LED or a dynamic Colour Change RGB LED to set the mood for your pool. The RGB model offers customizable lighting effects and can be seamlessly integrated with LumiPlus control systems like the LumiPlus Eco, Top, LED APP, and Modbus for full control of your pool’s lighting.
  • Elegant Design: Available with either a modern White Frame or a sophisticated Stainless Steel Frame, the LumiPlus Mini LED complements any pool design, adding a touch of elegance to your outdoor space.

Optimized for Pool Size

For optimal illumination, it’s recommended to install one LumiPlus Mini V2 LED light for every 5 m² of water surface area. This ensures that your pool is evenly lit, creating a stunning visual effect, whether you're going for a serene white glow or vibrant, colorful displays.

Upgrade your pool lighting with the LumiPlus Mini LED Swimming Pool Light—combining cutting-edge technology, energy efficiency, and timeless design for the perfect poolside experience.

Monaco Mobile Swimming Pool Reel System
Product Description:
Monaco Mobile Swimming Pool Reel System

The Monaco mobile swimming pool reel system is designed to enable the user to wind their pool cover on and off with minimum effort. Manufactured with high quality materials the Monaco reel system is available in two sizes depending on the width of the swimming pool: small 12'-15' (3.6 - 4.5m) or large 15'-21' (4.5 - 6.4m).

The Monaco uses a rigid telescopic tubing system, with a built-in locking system to brace the tube in place. The roller tube is supported by mirror-polished stainless steel legs, with an anti-reel locking system. Adjustable feet allow you to level the reel on uneven ground, and a luxury five-spoke wheel lets you operate the system.

All models of the Monaco swimming pool reel system are constructed with the following features:-

  • 1¾" Stainless steel stands
  • Grooved anodised aluminium tube for durability
  • Adjustable feet - ideal for uneven surfaces
  • Coaster bearings in the yoke enable easy winding of the cover
  • The Monaco reel system can also be floor or wall mounted

Monaco Swimming Pool Reel System

The Monaco reel system is available in one spec:-

  • Premier - fitted with a deluxe 5 spoke steering wheel and factory fitted smart gear enabling easier winding

Thetford Topline 111 Hob and Sink Campervan Conversion Kit 1
Product Description:
Thetford Topline 111 Hob and Sink Conversion Kit 1

With all you need for running water and gas cooking

This conversion kit is perfect for smaller campervans, giving you a compact and reliable water and gas set-up for your vehicle. This kit includes two jerry cans for fresh and waste water, as well as a tap, 12v pump and piping to complete the water system. A gas regulator and gas hose lets you connect your hobs to a gas cylinder safely, too.

Includes Thetford's modern Topline hob and sink

This kit uses Thetford's Topline 111 hob, which includes 12v ignition and a sleek glass lid to make campervan or motorhome feel complete. Two 1.5kW gas burners give you ample power for your cooking, and matt nickel control knobs let you adjust the gas output.

Product Description:
Platinum 110Ah Campervan Motorhome Caravan Leisure Battery

This 110Ah Lead acid leisure battery is ideal for your 12v Leisure power needs featuring a rapid recharge rate and is compatible with most modern intelligent charging units.

Ideal for use with our Solar Panel Kits

These Campervan, Motorhome, and Caravan Leisure batteries take kindly to a solar panel charging system, keeping the cells in good shape and keeping you topped up when off electric hookup.

Platinum 110Ah Leisure Battery for Campervan Motorhome and Caravan Features:-

  • A State of Charge Indicator allows an easy visual check of the charge and acid level of the leisure battery.
  • Constructed with Thick Grid Technology and glass fibre plate separators this increases the deep cycle capability, charge capacity, and vibration resistance which extends the service life of the Platinum 110Ah leisure battery.
  • The Labyrinth-Lid with a spark arrestor allows battery emissions to be vented externally from the campervan, motorhome or caravan and protects against gas ignition within the battery thus enabling the battery to be stored within living areas.

The Platinum 110Ah Leisure Battery should not be allowed to run flat and should be charged once a month when the battery is not in use.

Product Name: Thetford C503L Caravan & Motorhome Cassette Toilet
Product Description:
Thetford C503L Caravan Motorhome & Campervan Cassette Toilet

A high quality Cassette Toilet for use in caravan, campervan or motorhome the Thetford C503L fixed bench Cassette Toilet features a waste tank capacity of 19.7 litres and comes with the convenience of electric flush.

The built-in Cassette Toilet consists of two parts: a permanently installed toilet and a removable waste-holding tank. A useful 3 level indicator lets you know when the waste tank needs to be emptied -which is easily accessible through a small door on the outside of the motorhome, campervan or caravan via the optional access door 3.

Additionally, the Thetford C503L caravan and motorhome Cassette Toilet also benefits from a retractable handle on the holding tank and comes with wheels on the base to provide easy transportation. A removable working mechanism is also included with the C503L Cassette Toilet, making the inside of the tank easier to clean.

This terrific caravan and motorhome toilet from Thetford is suitable for installation against the external side wall or rear wall of the caravan, motorhome or campervan but can also be easily installed against an interior wall in your vehicle/vessel, provided there is level access on the other side, to enable the waste tank removal

Thetford C503L Caravan & Motorhome Cassette Toilet features.

  • 3 level waste holding tank level indicator
  • Waste holding tank on wheels
  • Vent plunger for easy emptying without splashing
  • Flush water taken from the vehicle's onboard tank
  • Electric push button flush -quiet yet powerful system with full bowl coverage - 12V Electric
  • Automatic pressure gas release vent
  • Available with the flush on the right or left hand side
  • 3 year warranty
  • **Please Note** This product usually requires the purchase of the Thetford 'Access Door' This provides neat access for removal of the waste tank.
  • Right handed model: If sat on the toilet the waste tank slides out to the Right.
  • Left handed model: If sat on the toilet the waste tank slides out to the Left.

Webasto Freeline Elegance 115L Compressor Caravan Motorhome Fridge
Product Description:
Webasto Freeline Elegance 115L Caravan, Motorhome & Campervan Compressor Fridge.

Versatile, Stylish and Frugal.

Representing an evolution of the Elegance line campervan, caravan and motorhome fridges, This fridge has been created, both for the Marine, & Campervan and caravan markets.  The Freeline 115's clever ITC (Intelligent Temperature Control) ECO feature stores refrigeration energy when a surplus of energy is available. This, combined with superior insulation, means the energy requirements of the refrigerator are 35% lower than existing fridges on the market.

A spacious cabinet - comprised of an 83 liter fridge and a 32 liter freezer.

The large fridges and freezer allow for perfect travel comfort. At least 4 carton boxes of pizza can be stored in the freezer as the compartment is developed on a full width design.  Characterized by a supreme cooling performance, the Freeline 115 reaches noticeable electrical efficiency.

The Webasto Freeline 115 Elegance is a caravan or marine fridge equipped with a modern control panel that includes Eco function

Eco function includes an overcooling mode (that stores energy in food & drinks if surplus of electricity is available); this Webasto caravan fridge allows easy operations, such as temperature setting, internal lighting and provides, by blinking code system for any failure in the useage.

Technical Details

  • Model: Freeline 115
  • Volume: 115 Litres
  • Dimensions (H x W X D) 797mm x 525mm x 498mm
  • Power Consumption (W/24hrs) 262 Watts (0.909ah @12v)
  • Weight (KG) 32kg
  • Silent, highly efficient, fan cooled 12/24V Danfoss / Secop compressor (type BD35F)
  • Control Panel Includes ECO function
  • Wide Freezer Compartment (32 litre Capacity)
  • Freezes to minus 8 degrees at 25 degrees ambient

Please note that the freezer compartment is only meant for short term storage of frozen food in a mobile setting, and will only freeze to minus 8 degrees.

If a true freezer to minus 18 degrees is required, please see the Waeco CRX140

Product Name: Webasto Cruise CR42 12volt 24v Small Compressor Marine Campervan Fridge
Product Description:
Webasto Cruise CR42 12/24 volt Compact Campervan Fridge

The Webasto C42 Elegance is the smallest 12 volt fridge of the Webasto Cruise range. This campervan fridge features a new inner lining with just the one adjustable shelf and two retainers inside the door, this small campervan fridge features a freezer compartment with a volume of 4 litres with magnetic steel evaporator door.

Back Mounted Compressor can be installed away from the fridge

On the back of the highly successful Cruise Elegance Line of campervan refrigerators, The Cruise CR42 Classic conveys all the Elegance line features, with the addition of the back mounted compressor being installed on a specially designed L bracket. This can then be installed up to 1 meter away from the cabinet!

Easy to install

The possibility to separate the condensing unit, associated with the low depth of the cabinet, make the isotherm Cruise 42 the best-balanced caravan campervan marine fridge in terms of outer dimension and inner space availability for food & drinks.


 

In the event that you require customer for support with this product, believing it to be faulty, the following process will allow for the quickest way for you, the customer, to obtain service.

  • Contact us at Jacksons Leisure to report an issue.
  • We will provide self-help troubleshooting advice.
  • If the issue is not solvable by self-help, then please visit this link, Webasto UK dealer locator. https://www.webasto.com/gb/dealerlocator/
  • Identify your local dealer and make contact.
  • You then take the product to the dealer for investigation / repair.
  • Warranty repairs will be billed by the dealer direct to Webasto 
  • Repairs which are outside of the warranty terms will be billed direct to you the customer.
  • Please note - the AC/DC model may come with a EU 2-pin plug, and as such you may need to use an adapter.

 

Please note: Due to the design of a fridge with a removable compressor, extra care must be taken when moving the fridge and demount-able compressor unit itself. The compressor can not be disconnected from the pipework.

The Propex electric water storage heater is a mains powered hot water heater designed for convenient hook-up use in your motorhome, campervan or caravan.   • Compact design - easy to mount in a locker, bedbox or under seat
  • Temperature meter with simple adjustment
  • The Propex water heater has protection against over temperature, over pressure and electricity leakage

The Webasto Marine Class Refrigerator

Product Name: Reimo MultiRail Awning Rail for VW T4 T5 T6 Campervans
Product Description:
Reimo Campervan Multi-purpose Awning Rail

High-quality awning rail for VW T4 T5 T6 Campervans & MPVs

The Reimo Multirail is one of the most versatile VW T4/T5/T6 awning rails on the market. The Reimo Multi-Rail acts not only a multi-purpose van rail, but also a gutter, thanks to its integrated grooves which allow your van to disperse rainwater easily. This means that you can open the doors of your vehicle without rain dripping on your head- it is instead channelled to the front and rear ends of the rail.

Robust construction

The Reimo awning rail is made from anodized aluminium, and has a sleek black finish to match any camper colour scheme. These stylistic features, combined with the complementary end profiles, give the awning rail a professional look.

You can also use the Reimo multi-rail campervan awning rail to fit a canopy or awning to the gutter by using a pole and clamps. A second channel for fitting your awning directly via a Kador strip makes it ideal for drive away awnings, too.

Reimo Campervan Awning Rail Features:

  • Dimensions short wheel base: 2.6 metres
  • Integrated gutter system
  • Compatible with roof racks
  • Suitable for loads of up to 100kg

This kit does NOT include the sealant - we recommend Sikaflex 221

CAN FL1766 - FL1765 2 Burner Hob  & Sink Camper Van Combination Unit
Product Description:
CAN Two Burner Hob & Sink Combination Unit With 2 Glass Lids

Sleek and compact burner and sink

The CAN double hob and sink with 2 glass lids is ideal for the tight spaces. CAN have designed this compact campervan hob and sink unit so you can maximise your work surface and the CAN hob and sink is smaller than Dometic Smev 9222 combination unit. So if you're working with a van conversion I'll space is really tight then this slim line two burner cooker and sink is an ideal solution for you!

With capable gas burners

This cooker includes both a 1.9kW and a 1kW gas burner, allowing you to rapidly fry and boil. The hob and sink can be concealed by the tempered black glass lids, allowing it to be used as a worktop, and soft-close hinges make them a joy to use. You can also choose for the sink and hob combi unit to be shipped with a suitable microswitched tap such as the Reich Samba.

CAN 2 burner hob & Sink Features:

  • Dimensions: Length: 765 mm; Depth: 355 mm; Height: 150 mm
  • Tap hole dimension: 33mm
  • NEW compact design CAN 2 burner hob/sink unit
  • Available in right and left hand (e.g. right has sink on right hand side)
  • Piezo Ignition
  • 2 Glass Lids
  • Note - supplied tap will be the Reich Samba, which has a slightly different profile of tap spout to the one in the pictures above
